These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: ship, quad-bike, scooter, bus, car, boat, roller
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, biathlon, cycling, parkour, skiing, volleyball
 1. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the bus and the person driving the roller##2
 2. the person driving the quad-bike is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person driving the car is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's sport is parkour##2
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 7. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
 8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 9. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
10. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
11. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Transport   | bus | ship | roller | quad-bike    | scooter | car   | boat    |
| Sport         | skiing  | baseball   | cycling | badminton | biathlon   | volleyball | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
There 7 different types of food: apple, cauliflower, grapefruit, grapes, lettuce, pomegranate, pumpkin
7 different pets are kept: ferret, snake, goldfish, mouse, rat, frog, goat
1. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is between the person eating pomegranate and the owner of the frog##2
3. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is in the middle##1
6. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
7. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
8. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
9. the person eating grapes is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Food          | lettuce | grapefruit | pomegranate | cauliflower | pumpkin | apple      | grapes  |
| Pet   | frog | mouse  | goat     | goldfish     | rat  | ferret | snake |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
7 different games are played: backgammon, monopoly, scrabble, snooker, domino, mah-jongg, go
7 different pets are kept: fish, goat, hamster, pony, rabbit, rat, turtle
 1. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 2. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 3. the owner of the rabbit is the person playing go##1
 4. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 5. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 6. the person playing snooker is the owner of the pony##1
 7. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 8. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the turtle and the person playing snooker##2
 9. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
10. the person playing monopoly is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Game   | go | domino | backgammon | monopoly   | snooker | scrabble | mah-jongg |
| Pet           | rabbit | rat     | goat     | hamster | pony   | fish   | turtle    |

