.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, juice, lemonade, sprite, tea, water
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: parkour, volleyball, golf, cycling, rugby, skateboarding, soccer
 1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person drinking juice and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
 7. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
10. the person who's sport is parkour is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | juice    | sprite  | lemonade  | fanta  | water      | tea       | iced-tea |
| Sport   | rugby | cycling | skateboarding | soccer | parkour | golf | volleyball  |

