.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
7 different games are played: backgammon, go, scrabble, mah-jongg, canasta, billiard, domino
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, motorbike, ship, skateboard, train, van
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is the person playing go##1
3. the person driving the bike is between the person playing domino and the person playing backgammon##2
4. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the train is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is the person playing mah-jongg##1
9. the person playing canasta is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Game   | mah-jongg      | canasta | backgammon | scrabble | domino      | go      | billiard |
| Transport     | helicopter | train | van       | bike | motorbike | skateboard | ship |

