.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  firefighter, paramedic, pilot, project-manager, scientist, videographer, writer
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: daffodil, aconite, poppy, iris, zinnia, rose, lily
1. the pilot is on the left of the writer##1
2. the person who growspoppy is the scientist##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
4. the paramedic is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
5. the videographer is on the right of the person who growslily##1
6. the person who growslily is between the person who growszinnia and the firefighter##2
7. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
8. the videographer is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | scientist | firefighter | project-manager | videographer | paramedic | pilot     | writer |
| Flower   | poppy   | iris    | lily    | zinnia      | aconite  | daffodil | rose |

