.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, lemonade, milk
House: farmhouse, cape-cod, colonial, craftsman, futuristic, ranch-style, modern
 1. the ranch-style house is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the modern house##1
 3. the cape-cod house is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking fanta is between the futuristic house and the modern house##2
 5. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
 7. the craftsman house is the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is the futuristic house##1
 9. the colonial house is between the futuristic house and the person drinking iced-tea##2
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | coffee | cola    | hot-chocolate | fanta   | lemonade | milk    | iced-tea |
| House      | craftsman | farmhouse | modern    | cape-cod | futuristic    | colonial | ranch-style  |

