 7. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 8. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking water and the person drinking cola##2
11. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
