3. the fan of indie is in the middle##1
4. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the fan of rock is between the person who's sport is tennis and the fan of jazz##2
7. the fan of house is between the fan of reggae and the fan of d&b##2
8. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
9. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | house       | reggae    | indie | rock | jazz     | ambient       |
| Sport   | lacrosse    | skateboarding | volleyball | tennis        | sailing | ice-hockey | weightlifting |

