.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-12::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: documentary, epic, horror, musical, spy, western, zombie
The people have 7 different hobbies: singing, dancing, cooking, hiking, fishing, traveling, rock-climbing
 1. the person watching documentary movies is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 2. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 3. the person watching documentary movies is between the person watching musical movies and the person who's hobby is singing##2
 4. the person watching western movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the person watching spy movies##2
 5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 7. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching horror movies is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left##1
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3   |   4   |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | documentary | epic  | spy   | western | zombie | horror |
| Hobby   | hiking     | rock-climbing       | singing | cooking | traveling  | dancing   | fishing   |

