The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: family, action, time-travel, horror, disaster, western, scientific
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, disco, house, indie, reggae, rock, trance
 1. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 2. the fan of disco is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 3. the person watching western movies is between the fan of ambient and the person watching disaster movies##2
 4. the person watching scientific movies is between the person watching horror movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
 5. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 6. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 7. the fan of house is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 8. the fan of trance is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 9. the fan of indie is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |      3      |   4    |    5    |   6   |    7     |
| Movie-Genre      | family   | time-travel | action | western | disaster | scientific   | horror |
| Music-Genre   | indie | house | ambient     | reggae | trance  | disco | rock     |

