 3. the person who's birthday is in march is the person eating apricot##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 6. the person eating carrot is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is the person eating orange##1
 8. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating orange##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person eating carrot##2
10. the person who's birthday is in january is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Birthday   | march   | february | july | january   | october   | november     | june  |
| Food       | apricot | lemon    | kiwi  | orange | banana | spinach | carrot |

